B.GZ=new A.dh('"Custom Linter Rules" article',"https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/C4E0BAQHUnHfOOcObCQ/company-logo_200_200/0/1622042907088?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=eJU3AidPOkPUi-rBHsv_wB0TE8RBDme_o80IXziVIvk","https://invertase.io/blog/custom-linter-rules","Custom linter rules can help ensure consistency across your codebase. By enforcing specific coding standards or best practices, you can ensure that all code is written in a similar style, making it easier to read and maintain.",null,null)
B.H2=new A.dh("Dart Functors, Applicatives, And Monads In Pictures","https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSU0rt-11RXA-gOhPqGHW7p1lOVVwwURmcKc_hQ0zNY7GZhVl--ekhupe3vgDTg_a3iE_M&usqp=CAU","https://olexale.medium.com/dart-functors-applicatives-and-monads-in-pictures-ddd8c54bce15","This is a translation of the Functors, Applicatives, And Monads In Pictures article from Haskell into Dart.",null,null)
B.GU=new A.dh("Custom Linter Rule for Dart Analyzer","","https://youtu.be/g9NAgb3KyaU","In this talk, explore how Dart's built-in rules improve developer efficiency and prevent early-stage mistakes. Learn how Flutter developers can extend these foundations with custom linter rules tailored to their team or project. We'll guide you through the process of creating a custom linter rule, both with simple and complex approaches.",null,!0)
B.GX=new A.dh("Private Dart and Flutter packages","","https://youtu.be/jfRhyAKzaBY","In this video, learn how to manage a mature Flutter project by dividing it into multiple packages. While referencing hosted packages from pub.dev is common, private packages may be necessary when open sourcing isn't an option. We'll demonstrate how to reference private packages and discuss the most convenient methods for working securely with confidential packages.",null,!0)
B.GW=new A.dh('"Enterprise Flutter" talk',"","https://youtu.be/lKpDigNCDi0","Explore the challenges of scaling Flutter projects as the number of developers increases in this talk. Learn about unbiased criteria for evaluating code simplicity and clarity, and delve into the agreements and approaches used in enterprise-sized projects. We'll discuss code metrics and the ones we collect, as well as provide practical tips and tricks that you can incorporate into your development process immediately.",null,!0)
B.H4=new A.dh('"Functional Dart" talk',"","https://youtu.be/p9dY-vp7xzY","Discover functional programming concepts like monads, currying, and functors without fear! These terms are no more intimidating than OOP jargon and were created to tackle real-world problems. Today's programming languages often incorporate functional paradigm elements. In this talk, learn helpful functional programming tips and tricks, for everyday tasks, along with popular packages that can streamline a developer's work.",null,!0)
B.GV=new A.dh("Flutter Europe talk","https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1167009161672122370/z3twWupL_400x400.jpg","https://youtu.be/lmiRYar996w","Flutter Europe uploaded a video with my talk. There is a cool story which happened right before the presentation in the comments \ud83d\ude05",null,null)
B.H3=new A.dh("BDD widget testing videos","","https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLjaSBcAZ8TqFx51f30aRi_A2szelttOpq","YouTube playlist with my live coding sessions on BDD in Flutter",null,!0)
B.H1=new A.dh("New article","https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/514769537195991040/YAJObmWx.png","https://www.itproportal.com/features/the-competitive-landscape-of-cross-platform-development-xamarin-flutter-and-react-native/",'My article "The competitive landscape of cross-platform development: Xamarin, Flutter and React Native" was published on ITProPortal! \ud83e\udd73',null,null)
B.GY=new A.dh("ARKit with Flutter tutorials","","https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MaH4L6R8ZfQ&list=PLjaSBcAZ8TqGoWj3FE96uQ2gGPDGaXbDp","AR might be tricky, especially when you're just starting. For those who want to add some augmented or virtual reality in their Flutter apps I've recorded a few short lessons.",null,!0)
B.H0=new A.dh("Flutter Courses","https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/50321121?s=200&v=4","https://twitter.com/OlexaLe/status/1192802637290360837","Yesterday we had the first exam in our Flutter course at Ciklum!\n\nSome stats: \n- we started with 142 students and 3 instructors \ud83e\udd2f\n- about 60 students worked through homework \u2328\ufe0f\n- 6 basic topics are done \ud83d\udc23, 14 advanced ahead!\ud83e\uddd9",null,null)
