B.DR=A.a(s(["Technical Leadership: Providing guidance and expertise on technical matters, ensuring that projects and systems are designed and implemented effectively and efficiently.","Architectural Design: Developing and maintaining the overall architecture of complex software systems, ensuring that they are scalable, secure, and maintainable.","Code Review: Reviewing and approving code changes submitted by team members, ensuring adherence to best practices, design patterns, and coding standards.","Mentorship: Supporting and mentoring engineers, helping them grow their skills and advance their careers.","Collaboration: Collaborating with cross-functional teams, including product management, quality assurance, and operations, to ensure that projects meet their goals and align with the organization's strategic objectives.","Problem Solving: Identifying and resolving complex technical issues, including debugging, performance optimization, and troubleshooting.","Research and Development: Staying current on emerging technologies and industry trends, and evaluating their potential application within the organization.","Process Improvement: Continuously evaluating and refining development processes, methodologies, and tools to enhance productivity and software quality."]),t.s)
B.A5=new A.e6("Senior Staff Engineer","Tide","dec 2021","present","My responsibilities are:",B.DR)
B.DV=A.a(s(["coordinate mobile tech.leaders and act as a consultant for mobile developers;","develop organizational policies and standards;","create quality targets and assure their appliance;","introduce new methodologies and tools, apply them on commercial projects;","act as a mobile stack expert during the sales process;","create learning programs, coordinate knowledge sharing activities;"]),t.s)
B.A7=new A.e6("Head of Mobile","Ciklum","april 2018","nov 2021","As a Head of Mobile Stack I:",B.DV)
B.Er=A.a(s(["I managed developers from iOS, Android, and cross-platform stacks. I owned the competence development process (assessment, education, certification, knowledge sharing, community development);","I responded for the alignment between personal development plans of each talent in the Mobile team with Ciklum's strategy;","Implemented a built-in quality approach across all mobile teams (including implementation of engineering practices, shared services, and technical audit process);"]),t.s)
B.A1=new A.e6("Mobile Technical Lead","Ciklum","january 2017","april 2018","While still acting as a cross-platform mobile developer, I had more administrative activities.",B.Er)
B.CI=A.a(s(["I developed cross-platform mobile applications in C#. Worked with F#, Objective-C, Swift, and Java. My target OS were iOS, Android, WP7, WP8, and UWP (Windows 10). Frameworks I used: Xamarin, Xamarin.Forms, FreshMvvm, Reactive Extensions, ReactiveProperty, RxUI, MvvmCross. I worked via TDD using NUnit, MSTest, and Moq. For a few projects used BDD with Calabash and Ruby. I acted as the chief reviewer during code reviews.","My primary responsibilities were team coaching and technical quality assurance. I improved and automated the internal processes: CI, metrics, workflows, and other best practices. I have conducted internal and external interviews.","I made estimations, participated in workshops, project, and proposal reviews. Supervised and participated in technology investigations and researches. Consulted client-side developers, responded for high-level architecture for projects."]),t.s)
B.A4=new A.e6("Xamarin Lead Dev","Ciklum","november 2012","december 2016","On this position, I was in charge not only for the software development but for the team.",B.CI)
B.Dx=A.a(s(["I started as a cross-platform mobile developer in C++ with the Marmalade SDK framework.","Soon I switched to C# and focused on young frameworks MonoTouch and MonoDroid, which became a foundation of the Xamarin platform afterward.","I developed a social network and a simple game for a brand new phone promotion."]),t.s)
B.A2=new A.e6("Cross-platform Developer","Ciklum","july 2012","november 2012","I was in charge for mobile application development.",B.Dx)
